PARAM.name: INPUT:POS
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Search position in the form RA,DEC in decimal degrees

PARAM.name: INPUT:SIZE
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Search region size in the RA,DEC directions in decimal degrees

PARAM.name: INPUT:LIMIT
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Maximum rows returned from the database

PARAM.name: INPUT:RENDERER
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Format to render the results of the query

FIELD.name: Axis Length
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Length in pixels of each image axis

FIELD.name: Axis Scale
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Image scaling factor, in degrees per pixel, of each image axis

FIELD.name: Image URL
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: URL to be used to access image file for this image
